	<yield_count>6</yield_count>
	<yield_measure>servings</yield_measure>
	<notes>I imagine "La Scala" as being That Place on the Lake Almanor Peninsula back in 1978.

I'll say that this recipe has a distinct "almost healthy except for that huge gob of olive oil bit."</notes>
	<ingredients>
		<ingredient>
			<quantity>24</quantity>
